    "rationale": "Despite all 13 credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels, and 6 factors remaining unassessed as epistemic gaps, the assessment team accepted the package for submission as a complete documentation of the credibility gap at MRL 5. The decision reflects acceptance of the evidence package as a formal record, not acceptance that the model is fit for the VAD COU. Regulatory submission will flag all gaps for FDA review. Note: the ContextOfUse does not specify applicability constraints or an operating envelope, leaving the valid range of model use uncharacterized.",
